descriptionHtml:
UPDATE APRIL 2013. The MAIN file is the OLD Original Textures Pack List. Obviously the one for 2013 is newer...

Don\'t be a moron. This isn\'t a mod. Don\'t download it with NMM and expect it to DO anything. Also, if you\'re a modder PLEASE read my NMM compatibility guide...

FIRST...for those NOT knowing.. the HiRes packs ONLY contain texture files. Modders looking for meshes and scripts need my other original list along with PICS of a lot of em.

I would have added them here but on 56k it took me 4 hours to upload the other one so...those of you priveledged peeps with DSL and FIOS can DL and UPload superquick. I, alas... cannot.

This is a text file of all textures from Bethesda\\\'s high res texture packs. I am working on separate breakdowns of ALL the main BSA files but give me time. I\'m on a single core 1meg ram 64k vid card laptop that BARELY runs skyrim.

I MAY upload my modified BSA files to nexus.  The ones that actually ALLOW me to play Skyrim on this old machine at 12fps average to 30fps in some places. I\'m on a 1gig machine Single core Intel with a 64k integrated video and sound.
author: Thorne67
